{"tid":1838538,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回力鏢]有酒店被指禁員工戴口罩　酒店業主聯會稱指控嚴重不實","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T05:23:06.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ddc349067543b7669efd1b7aa71ee1879ae1165","tid":1838538,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:13:42.000Z","msg":"香港酒店工會早前表示，有酒店口頭禁止前線員工工作時戴口罩，是罔顧員工及客人的生命安全和健康。香港酒店業主聯會發聲明說，這是嚴重不實的指控，嚴厲譴責有關指控影響業界聲譽和國際的信心。<br />\n<br />\n聯會說，在本港發現新型冠狀病毒確診個案後，已向會員轉發衞生防護中心對酒店業的指引，強調業界視員工為重要資產，置旅客和員工的安全在首位。聯會表示會密切留意事態發展，提醒會員做好防護措施。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母，呢封email假架?定萬麗唔係香港酒店?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200113/large/1578843717_f74e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200113%2Flarge%2F1578843717_f74e.jpg&h=62c62257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200113/QUL57RJ57ZTKVO2JAZGCLFXMCA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200113%2FQUL57RJ57ZTKVO2JAZGCLFXMCA%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXyfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=5c03bc3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200113%2FQUL57RJ57ZTKVO2JAZGCLFXMCA%2F&h=1e1123f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200113/QUL57RJ57ZTKVO2JAZGCLFXMCA/</a><br />\n<br />\n接待武漢旅客 <br />\n萬麗禁員工戴口罩"},{"pid":"6ab4edfcfecb3b2f3e9dbb8cc06b93bbdbbd2dc5","tid":1838538,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:14:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<b